My name is D.J. Rhino.

01:58:29.110 --> 01:58:31.110
I can left and right for a cereal that won't boil me,

01:58:31.110 --> 01:58:32.110
but there isn't one inside.

01:58:32.110 --> 01:58:33.110
Well, don't use your eyes.

01:58:33.110 --> 01:58:36.110
Just follow your nose to a fruit-flavored surprise.

01:58:36.110 --> 01:58:37.110
Kellogg's Fruit Loop Cereal.

01:58:37.110 --> 01:58:38.110
Papa Fruit Loops.

01:58:38.110 --> 01:58:39.110
Orange.

01:58:39.110 --> 01:58:40.110
Lemon.

01:58:40.110 --> 01:58:41.110
Cherry and lime.

01:58:41.110 --> 01:58:42.110
Part of a complete breakfast.

01:58:42.110 --> 01:58:43.110
That really makes them bite.

01:58:43.110 --> 01:58:45.110
I bought a colorful breakfast.

01:58:45.110 --> 01:58:46.110
Another Fruit Loop plan.

01:58:46.110 --> 01:58:47.110
And I got great taste.

01:58:47.110 --> 01:58:48.110
Like me to dance to them.

01:58:48.110 --> 01:58:51.110
Yo, Santa, you're totally fresh.

01:58:51.110 --> 01:58:57.650
We paid up.

01:58:57.650 --> 01:59:01.220
When you talk into Starlo's magic microphone,

01:59:01.220 --> 01:59:03.220
she says what you say in her own voice.

01:59:03.220 --> 01:59:04.220
Let's sing a song.

01:59:04.220 --> 01:59:05.220
You can sing along.

01:59:05.220 --> 01:59:07.220
I like to sing with you.

01:59:07.220 --> 01:59:08.220
Nobody sounds like you, Starlo.

01:59:08.220 --> 01:59:09.220
We like to show off.

01:59:09.220 --> 01:59:10.220
Starlo.

01:59:10.220 --> 01:59:11.220
Like it's Starlo.

01:59:11.220 --> 01:59:12.220
I love it.

01:59:12.220 --> 01:59:13.220
Hey, she's talking.

01:59:13.220 --> 01:59:14.220
She's Starlo.

01:59:14.220 --> 01:59:18.220
Wherever we go, we burn on a shot.

01:59:18.220 --> 01:59:19.220
Starlo comes with a magic microphone

01:59:19.220 --> 01:59:21.220
so you can give her a voice on her own.

01:59:21.220 --> 01:59:22.220
Batteries not included.

